===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|Χριστόφορος||Christ-bearing}}. The meaning of the name suggested the legend of St. Christopher carrying the Christ child across water.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈkɹɪs.tə.fə(ɹ)/|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈkɹɪs.tə.fɚ/|lang=en}}

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

